      <title>迪拜亿万富翁的儿童计划重振陷入困境的世界岛屿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/dubai-real-estate-damac-billionaire-s-children-launch-world-islands-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，这座以世界地图形状建造的人工群岛被视为迪拜过度发展的象征，正是这种过度发展导致迪拜濒临破产。现在，一位亿万富翁开发商的子女正试图用 1360 万美元起的海滨豪宅重振该项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/dubai-real-estate-damac-billionaire-s-children-launch-world-islands-project</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:11:02 GMT</pubDate>
